item.description:
The hint:
&lt;!-- No more information leaks!! Not even Google will find it this time... --&gt; I completely randomly tried to check the robots.txt file&hellip;
URL=http://natas3.natas.labs.overthewire.org curl --user natas3:$(cat natas3) $URL&#34;/robots.txt&#34; There I found /s3cr3t/ which then led me to the /s3cr3t/users.txt file with the password for natas4. In the hindsight I get it &ldquo;Not even Google&rdquo; web crawlers will find it. Robots.txt is a informational file for web crawlers to see what they should index or not&hellip;
